prompts.frontCover: Minimalist 2D cartoon illustration for a funny birthday greeting card. The scene is set on a bright, sunny beach with a clean, flat design and a soft color palette. In the center, there is a large sandcastle cleverly shaped like a classic Chinese takeout box, complete with a wire handle made of seaweed. Atop the sandcastle walls, boba pearls are piled up like cannonballs. Defending the sandcastle is a tiny, charming cartoon figure of a girl, poised to launch a boba pearl from a toy catapult. Approaching the sandcastle is an army of small, humorous red crabs. Each crab brandishes a pair of chopsticks like a weapon, marching in a funny, disorganized line. The entire scene is depicted with simple shapes, clean lines, and a lighthearted feel. Centered in the sky above the action, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script.
